title: East Boca Raton Townhouse
posting_body: ['Rarely found 2-story townhouse in East Boca Raton close to Florida Atlantic University (FAU).', '2 bedrooms/3 bathrooms.', '1,428 sqft total or 1,335 sqft interior livable area.', 'Screened patio, storage room, etc. Central AC.', 'Washer/dryer.', 'Brand new ceilings and walls, brand-new range/oven, brand-new shower, new metal roof, etc.', 'Fenced backyard.', 'Downstairs: full kitchen, living room, bathroom, storage rooms, outside screened patio & little front porch.', 'Upstairs: 2 spacious bedrooms, large walk-in closets, 2 full bathrooms, washer/dryer in between, providing great privacy for both bedrooms.', 'Carpet on 2nd floor but pretty new.', 'Walk to FAU and beautiful El Ril Canal and Trail (2.5 miles).', 'A+ public schools (Boca Middle and High Schools; JC Mitchell Elementary; FAU K-12 Schools.', 'According to 2022 Florida public school rankings, FAU K-12 Schools are ranked No. 2 for Best Public Elementary School, No. 2 for Best Public Middle School, and No. 2 for Best Public High School in State of Florida!', 'Our townhouse is only 3 mins walking to these schools).', 'Preschool on the street.', 'Minutes to (free) public beaches and parks, grocery (Costco, Walmart, Publix, Whole Foods, incoming ALDE, etc), downtown, hospitals, I-95, etc.', 'Close to everything.', 'Ample parking (2+ parking).', 'Swimming pool.', 'Quite and gardening space in backyard.', 'Pet friendly.', 'Monthly rent $2,700, or best offer.', 'If interested, please contact owner by text', 'show contact info', ').']
